{
  "texts": [
    "We discussed how giving the explanatory decision power to the decision subject, can in turn create new issues.",
    "Some of these issues could potentially be solved by developing new algorithms that can combine many counterfactual explanations into one.",
    "However, this may cause the problem to simply move to the level of algorithms that combine these counterfactual explanations.",
    "Therefore, we argue that currently, the most viable solution might be to provide transparency.",
    "Decision makers should document all decisions that led to the explanations."
  ]
}